utterances: kya mere lie portal se meri complaint hatana possible hai?

WOMEN/CHILD se RELATED CRIME section ke tahat file ki gai complaint ko vapas lena possible nahi hai. FIR men transformed hone se pahale, REPORT OTHER CYBER CRIME section ke tahat file ki gai complaint ko withdraw kiya ja sakata hai.
Hash value ka purpose kya hai?

ek hash value ek fixed-length ka alpha-numeric value hai jo aapke dvara portal men evidence ke roop men upload ki gai digital asset (jaise images, videos, documents, aadi) ke lie ek unique fingerprint/ number ke roop men kam karata hai.  hash value portal par aapke dvara upload kie gae kisi bhi digital evidence ki integrity ensure karata hai.
